Dialogue: 0,0:00:07.75,0:00:13.53,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Chystám se oženit s tím, koho miluji.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:17.74,0:00:21.12,main,Aizo,0,0,0,,Hledal jsem tě dlouho předtím, než jsme se potkali.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:22.21,0:00:24.50,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Cože? Dva ženichové?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:28.50,0:00:30.76,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Someya-kun? Shibasaki-kun?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:31.83,0:00:32.98,main,Aizo,0,0,0,,Miluji tě.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:32.98,0:00:33.84,main,Yujiro,0,0,0,,Miluji tě.
Dialogue: 0,0:00:34.14,0:00:34.91,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:35.62,0:00:36.34,main,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Cože?!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:37.08,0:00:38.04,main,Aizo,0,0,0,,Vezmeš...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:38.04,0:00:38.91,main,Yujiro,0,0,0,,Vezmeš...
Dialogue: 0,0:00:39.35,0:00:40.87,main,Aizo & Yujiro,0,0,0,,...si mě?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:52.82,0:00:53.49,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Cože?
Dialogue: 0,0:00:53.49,0:00:56.70,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Počkejte... Počkejte chvíli!
Dialogue: 0,0:00:57.33,0:00:58.28,italics,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Počkejte—
Dialogue: 0,0:01:04.37,0:01:06.96,main,Hiyori,0,0,0,,B-byl to sen...
Dialogue: 0,0:01:07.47,0:01:10.51,main,Hiyori,0,0,0,,Proč se mi to zdálo?!
Dialogue: 0,0:01:10.96,0:01:14.47,OP_ED,,0,0,0,,I'm charmed by how you go all-out
Dialogue: 0,0:01:14.47,0:01:18.97,OP_ED,,0,0,0,,I'm charmed by your supportive smile
